summary: Just a Daedric Sword called Azura's Butter Knife, it does 129 damage and absorbs 30 points of stamina.
descriptionHtml:
Have you ever wondered what a Daedric Sword's true purpose is? Or perhaps what the Daedra use to cut butter? No? Well look no further because Azura's Butter Knife has been found in the depths of Blackreach though don't hit anyone you love with it...

Just a Daedric Sword called Azura's Butter Knife, it does 129 damage and absorbs 30 points of stamina.
To get it type in the console: player.additem 53000d62
author: JuviaLockser5463
